{"list":[{"title":"目的","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">观察静电感应现象。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"原理","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">同种电荷相互排斥，异种电荷相互吸引。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"器材","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">带绝缘座的金属箔导体、带正电的小球。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"步骤","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">1<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">．拖动带正电的小球靠近导体</span>A<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">但不要接触，观察金属箔的变化；</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">2<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">．向右拖动导体</span>B<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">使</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">A</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">B</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">分开，观察现象；</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">3<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">．移走带正电的小球，观察现象；</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">4<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">．拖动并将</span>A<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">B</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">合上，观察现象。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"结论","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">拖动带正电的小球靠近导体</span>A<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">时，金属箔张开；向右拖动导体</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">B</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">使</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">A</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">B</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">分开，金属箔仍张开；移走带正电的小球，金属箔仍张开；拖动并将</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">A</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">B</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">合上金属箔仍闭合</span></span></span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"补充","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">当一个带电体靠近导体时，由于电荷间的相互作用，导体中的电荷会发生重新排布，靠近带电体的一端带异号电荷，远离带电体的一端带同号电荷。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>"}],"x":0,"y":0,"width":600,"height":600}